  "text": "Data collection. The demographic data included the age, sex, body mass index, functional capacity in activities of daily living (ADL) prior to hospitalization (Katz index [CITATION_1] ), history of aspiration, residence, use of tube feeding or parenteral nutrition, extent of alcohol intake (heavy alcohol consumption; .80 g daily), comorbidities assessed by the Charlson Comorbidity Index (CCI) [CITATION_2] , immunosuppressive state [CITATION_3] , and regular medication.",
